    The XXGGeettVViissuuaallIInnffoo function returns a list of visual structures that have
    attributes equal to the attributes specified by vinfo_template. If no
    visual structures match the template using the specified vinfo_mask,
    XXGGeettVViissuuaallIInnffoo returns a NULL. To free the data returned by this function,
    use XXFFrreeee.

    The XXMMaattcchhVViissuuaallIInnffoo function returns the visual information for a visual
    that matches the specified depth and class for a screen. Because multiple
